text: Mikhaylovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Mikhaylovsky Selsoviet, Limansky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,165 as of 2010. There are 23 streets. == Geography == It is located 120 km from Astrakhan, 21 km from Liman. == References == Category:Rural localities in Limansky District
title: Mikhaylovka, Limansky District, Astrakhan Oblast
